00:40:14.810 --> 00:40:19.940
And the zinc was being oxidized,
generating electrons, which

00:40:19.940 --> 00:40:21.830
come around to the copper.

00:40:21.830 --> 00:40:24.590
And then the copper
plus 2 ions were

00:40:24.590 --> 00:40:26.840
being reduced to copper solid.

00:40:26.840 --> 00:40:30.710
So the zinc anode
